{"tid":2447541,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"TSLA係唔係史上最多人唱衰既公司？","createTime":"2021-03-15T09:03:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-15T15:21:09.000Z","uid":37146,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"0ddb57e185bbd35485fcfb7985c0372a6aebe4a2","tid":2447541,"uid":37146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T09:03:54.000Z","msg":"日日都有黑鳩TSLA既新聞<br />\n<span class=\"violet\"><strong>媒體瘋狂唱衰</strong></span><br />\n工廠肺炎爆發<br />\n工廠發生火災<br />\n老細玩幣被查<br />\n股東告鳩老細<br />\n不受控制撞車<br />\n電池突然自燃<br />\n做工質素參差<br />\n回收車輛調查<br />\n產能進度緩慢<br />\n自動駕駛落後<br />\n市場份額被搶<br />\n股價估值過高<br />\n等等...<br />\n<br />\n之前有冇其他企業係咁？蘋果，亞馬遜都好似冇乜人唱衰<br />\n<br />\n係咪馬仔得罪人多定特斯拉真係咁差？"},{"pid":"a47f49a1227d7d0bf7cf7f204d3ba1ead7d6ce7b","tid":2447541,"uid":8113,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T09:05:08.000Z","msg":"人地講事實，佢升係因為對 Elon 有信念。"},{"pid":"6d9abee6e13e81f73a30fe5ff07ed263212b3c81","tid":2447541,"uid":75372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T09:06:15.000Z","msg":"比特幣先係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19c6473154fe8ffdc528f1e673c767ee5b93a436","tid":2447541,"uid":295230,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T09:06:48.000Z","msg":"aapl同amzn十年前咪都係一樣被瘋狂唱衰"},{"pid":"db2645cf670b7fd8f7b00d7987428fd602608b98","tid":2447541,"uid":255650,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6d9abee6e13e81f73a30fe5ff07ed263212b3c81","tid":2447541,"uid":75372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T09:06:15.000Z","msg":"比特幣先係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T09:06:52.000Z","msg":"公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bf36d8876e805c2649974094f4663fc2f4e7baa","tid":2447541,"uid":75372,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"db2645cf670b7fd8f7b00d7987428fd602608b98","tid":2447541,"uid":255650,"like"